- In the refrigerator.

715
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:44,160
Wait a minute.

716
00:39:50,520 --> 00:39:52,440
How do you live like this?

717
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:54,400
Wait a minute.

718
00:40:23,120 --> 00:40:24,520
Done.

719
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:27,840
