720
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:28,760
Here.

721
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,080
Chopsticks.

722
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:34,360
You made this cup noodles

723
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,520
