730
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:53,360
Tasty.

731
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:58,360
Make yourself at home.

732
00:40:59,720 --> 00:41:00,560
Okay.

733
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:06,480
How tasty.

734
00:41:20,240 --> 00:41:21,080
Ruoxin.

